title: Is Amy Too Old to Wear Abercrombie?  + Listener in A Shady Situation with Christmas Gift + Country Artist ‘Jingle Bells’ Game
itunes:title: Is Amy Too Old to Wear Abercrombie?  + Listener in A Shady Situation with Christmas Gift + Country Artist ‘Jingle Bells’ Game
description:
Amy went to the mall to shop with her daughter and ended up buying herself some clothes from Abercrombie. She debates if she’s too old to wear it… A listener calls in asking for advice after he received 6 tablets when he only ordered 1. We play a fun Christmas game where we try to guess the country artist singing Jingle Bells!
